text:
the frames i ordered were "over sized" for shipping. there was an additional charge. the packaged arrived via ups with two large gouges in the side of the box. the additional packaging material kept the frames safe and unharmed. the packaging was great. everything all 6 frames arrived in perfect condition.
thanks for the extra attention to detail.
